    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE029">
<l>yaraḻa veṉṉum puḷḷi muṉṉar</l>
<l>mutalā keḻuttu ṅakaramoṭu tōṉṟum</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>After the single consonants <foreign xml:lang="ta">y, r, ḻ,</foreign></l>
<l>the initial sounds and <foreign xml:lang="ta">ṅ</foreign> also appear.<note
              place="foot">The ' initial sounds ' <foreign xml:lang="ta">(mutalākeḻuttu)</foreign> are the 9 consonants which may occur initially in the language of <foreign xml:lang="ta">Tolk.</foreign>,
          i.e. <foreign xml:lang="ta">k, c, ñ, t, n, p, m, y, v.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
